WEBVTT

00:07:38.692 --> 00:07:41.087
PC: Sorry about that.
I needed to get a reaction.

00:07:41.111 --> 00:07:42.896
(Laughter)

00:07:43.412 --> 00:07:48.384
I'm actually tracking the carbon dioxide
you exhale in the room right now.

00:07:49.903 --> 00:07:53.196
We've installed tubes
throughout the theater,

00:07:53.220 --> 00:07:55.815
lower to the ground,
because CO2 is heavier than air.

00:07:55.839 --> 00:07:58.506
But they're connected
to a device in the back

00:07:58.530 --> 00:08:01.817
that lets us measure, in real time,
with high precision,